        <tr>
            <td colspan="4">
                <b>*</b><br>
                <b>Rerata Rapor</b> = (I + II + III + IV + V + VI) / 6;<br>
                <b>Nilai Sekolah</b> = (60% X Rerata Rapor) + (40% X
